# Unit 3 — *My digital detox* (games & speaking)

Data lives under `unit3-digital-detox/data/`. Game pages under `unit3-digital-detox/games/`. Text hub: `unit3-digital-detox/index.html`. **Exam mode (FCE/CAE-style Reading Part 5, 1–6 A–D):** `unit3-digital-detox/exam-mode-reading-p5.html` with data + distractor copy in `data/u3-reading-part5-exam.js` (separate from `games/`). **Bank of lexical games (tab):** `unit3-digital-detox/lexical-games-digital-detox.html` + `word-bank-digital-detox.html` — FCE Unit 3 only; must not be wired into `index.html` Unit 9 / CPE Word Bank; see **`.cursor/rules/u3-lexical-games-bank.mdc`**.

## Game registry (logics in short)

1. **Millionaire ×3** — `u3-games-content.js` (`U3_MILLIONAIRE_FACTS`, `GAPS`, `PARAPHRASE`). Hint iframe: `U3_sourceFileForTopic` → paths are `../text-0N-digital-detox.html` (pages in `games/`).
2. **Weakest link** — `U3_WEAKEST_LINK_POOL`
3. **Tic-tac** — `U3_TIC_TAC_POOL` (gaps) + `U3_sourceFileForTopic` for text hint
4. **100 to 1** — `U3_HUNDRED_ROUNDS` (hint paths `../text-0N-...`)
5. **Glass bridge** — `U3_GLASS_STEPS` (`source` with `../`)
6. **Red / green** — `U3_RED_GOOD`, `U3_RED_BAD` (phrases from unit, silly decoys only — do not mix other course units)
7. **Speaking squad, Names** — `u3-digital-detox-lexis.js` (`U3_DIGITAL_DETOX_PHRASES`)
8. **Alias, Pictionary, Whisper, What’s missing, Snowball** — same lexis file + missing/snowball arrays where listed in that file
9. **Domino** — `u3-domino-deck.js`
10. **Eco-Uno** — `u3-eco-uno-digital-detox.js` (phrases from text only, no random copy)
11. **Memory pairs** — `u3-memory-pairs.js`: phrase ↔ gloss; **9 pairs = 18 cards** per game; `random` 9 of 18, or `Set A` (pairs 1–9) / `Set B` (10–18); grid 6×3 / 3×6, numbers on back for class call-outs
12. **Part → thesis** — `u3-part-thesis-match.js`: **6** one-line theses, match to **Part 1…6** (structure / gist, *not* key-phrase ↔ gloss). Click thesis, then Part; Reset clears; Shuffle reorders theses and clears
13. **Pair questions** — `u3-pair-prompts.js` (EN-only UI; `tip` in English)

## Rules when adding content

- Keep all Unit 3 game copy **in-theme** (digital / phone / habits). No environmental or other-unit leaks in decoys.
- New games: add data in `data/*.js`, one HTML in `games/`, link from `games/index.html` and mention in text hub if major.
- Iframe and static text links from `games/*.html` must use `../` to reach `text-0N-digital-detox.html`.
